<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>اختتنَ يختتن، اختتانًا، فهو مختتِن، والمفعول مُختتَن <span class="c2">(للمتعدِّي)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• اختتن الصَّبيُّ:</span> قُطعت قُلْفَتُه.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• اختتن الصَّبيَّ:</span> قطع قُلْفَتَه.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>